      <p>You can edit the Qualification and Benefits page when the program is in In Amendment status.</p>
      <p>You can perform one or more of the actions listed below:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>Duplicating a section</li>
         <li>Deleting a section</li>
         <li>Adding a new section</li>
         <li>Deleting a row</li>
         <li>Adding new products (qualification as well as benefits)</li>
         <li>Importing and exporting product rows</li>
      </ul>
      <p>The following action is restricted on the qualification and benefits page while amending the program.</p>
      <ul>
         <li>Editing the start date and end date on existing product rows</li>
      </ul>
